 sea salt, plus extra for sprinkling"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 pinch ground white pepper"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1000 g vegetable oil"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 limes, halved"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"200 g sweet chilli dipping sauce"}],"nutrition":["per 1 piece","66.4 kJ \/ 15.9 kcal","0.1 g","0.3 g","1.6 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["The quantity of oil needed for frying will vary according to the size of your frying pan. It should be approx. <b>2 cm<b> deep in the pan.","To test the temperature of the oil, and the seasoning of the prawn mixture, carefully drop one teaspoon of mixture in the pan, it should fry quickly. Remove with a slotted spoon, cool slightly then taste, adjusting seasoning of fritters if desired."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","55m","24 pieces"]}